,"location":2,"to":1281.89},{"content":"-能想像到吧 -那畫面簡直清晰可見","from":1281.89,"location":2,"to":1283.55},{"content":"沒錯 就是在大家熱熱鬧鬧跳盂蘭盆舞的時候","from":1283.66,"location":2,"to":1287.56},{"content":"在離會場稍微有些距離的地方","from":1287.72,"location":2,"to":1290.34},{"content":"獨自二人倚靠在樹蔭下的長椅上望著會場談天這樣","from":1290.34,"location":2,"to":1297.58},{"content":"小優的表情已經…","from":1297.84,"location":2,"to":1298.88},{"content":"共度只屬於兩個人的時間","from":1298.88,"location":2,"to":1300.31},{"content":"怎麼樣 小優","from":1301.85,"location":2,"to":1302.85},{"content":"棒極了","from":1303.03,"location":2,"to":1304.16},{"content":"無與倫比","from":1305.8,"location":2,"to":1306.73},{"content":"聽了剛才的描述我想到了","from":1307.47,"location":2,"to":1309.16},{"content":"這種節慶活動不都是熙熙攘攘的嗎","from":1309.47,"location":2,"to":1312.19},{"content":"所以總有一種會走散的感覺","from":1312.68,"location":2,"to":1315.21},{"content":"這時候就抓住走在前面的喜歡的人的袖口","from":1315.98,"location":2,"to":1319.73},{"content":"-太美妙了 -兩個人一起前往那個神社 -謝謝","from":1320.25,"location":2,"to":1324.08},{"content":"然後","from":1324.83,"location":2,"to":1325.48},{"content":"還有然後啊","from":1325.48,"location":2,"to":1326.11},{"content":"然後 然後…","from":1326.11,"location":2,"to":1327.14},{"content":"然後他說「再抓緊一些」","from":1327.26,"location":2,"to":1329.46},{"content":"然後一把扯過去","from":1329.76,"location":2,"to":1330.79},{"content":"然後就會手牽手了","from":1331.02,"location":2,"to":1331.81},{"content":"會手牽手！","from":1331.81,"location":2,"to":1332.8},{"content":"好 謝謝大家","from":1333.12,"location":2,"to":1334.51},{"content":"太棒了","from":1334.69,"location":2,"to":1335.45},{"content":"我贏啦","from":1335.7,"location":2,"to":1336.38},{"content":"非常感謝","from":1336.38,"location":2,"to":1337.69},{"content":"在人飽心也飽之後 便是久候了多時的…","from":1338.9,"location":2,"to":1343.33},{"content":"來啦！","from":1345.58,"location":2,"to":1346.56},{"content":"好可愛","from":1346.56,"location":2,"to":1347.64},{"content":"太漂亮了","from":1348.48,"location":2,"to":1349.4},{"content":"太棒了","from":1351.84,"location":2,"to":1352.53},{"content":"燒得好劇烈","from